data.description: Welcome to a fantastic opportunity in the midst of a desired area and an award-winning school district! Don't miss this opportunity to own a 5.22 acre estate lot in Suwanee. Low Maintenance 4 sided brick home has 3 bedroom 3 bath and partially finished basement with potentially 2 extra bedrooms and exterior entrance. You will find this home nestled on a private lot and surrounded by an established neighborhood and newer million dollar plus homes. So many possibilities to update, build your dream home or add to your investment portfolio. You must visit to see the opportunities for this property. No HOA. This home boasts both privacy and community. Located near Downtown Suwanee, George Pierce Park, restaurants, excellent schools and shopping.
